cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "llm_bridge"
abstract: >-
  A tiny, vendor-neutral wrapper for any LLM backend: one interface (LLMClient)
  with pluggable adapters for OpenAI, AWS Bedrock, and Google Gemini, plus a
  callable provider to bring your own backend. The core install has zero
  required dependencies.
type: software
authors:
